high_descs: Turn to the right and walk straight to the small black shelf to the left of the counter.
Pick up the green apple from the shelf.
Move to the right to face the sink.
Place the apple in the sink, run some water, then pick up the apple.
Move to the left to face the black shelf.
Place the apple on the black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed apple on the black shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to face the black table.
Pick up the apple on the black table.
Step to the right to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Step to the left to face the black table.
Place the apple on the black table.
anns.task_desc: To clean an apple and put it back in it's spot.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black table in the left corner of the room.
Take a few steps right to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Take a few steps left back to the table.
Place the apple on the table to the left of the black container.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple on a table.
